{"tid":1524641,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"柴灣街坊入 地鐵站出咗藍旗","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:56:58.000Z","uid":227929,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"12edb3e464f08b346779d9c088c33794c67eb2d6","tid":1524641,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVEAjKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVEAjKQ.jpg&h=32b94947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柴灣地鐵站0050左右有full gear 狗入內截查站內接放學既手足。消息指徐子見被捕。<br />\n<br />\n事件起因：<br />\n今晚較早時，有熱心人喺柴灣站等候接放學<br />\n頭先地鐵停駛後，仍然有熱心人留守等緊翻黎既手足<br />\n有乘客因為不滿意港鐵突然停駛而去客務中心同職員理論，維持左1+ hour<br />\n有理由相信職員因此報驚。<br />\n<br />\n人數：接放學手足不只徐子見一個。實數不透露。"},{"pid":"435c33515b00627991c53ace95e57a1acfb924c3","tid":1524641,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:45:59.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70ma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=cd7d2ae5\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70ma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=a47d7f49\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70ma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=537d928c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"5fa421dd6845ed063412dd7e575e6df919e64222","tid":1524641,"uid":93908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:46:32.000Z","msg":"一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：［901入機場］今日重演721，黑警太子版核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！"},{"pid":"c6bddbed8ad65c5d9b095b77f053e784cd605a98","tid":1524641,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6238c3925720b7238050b0d107e03e6a9dd46407","tid":1524641,"uid":81385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:47:48.000Z","msg":"push請開live"},{"pid":"3ad8880651fbb31bd0ae42e814470a3076cdac56","tid":1524641,"uid":288408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"095b9214ffc88da423bcb2aa0ea9904670de1b17","tid":1524641,"uid":214177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:48:44.000Z","msg":"要唔要人?"},{"pid":"203f83f8a1837efb65e4a9ddccdf4894c5da3008","tid":1524641,"uid":222451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e59P8v3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe59P8v3.jpg&h=4577f61c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1AsaKo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1AsaKo.jpg&h=5c61cb03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請轉至Twitter同Reddit"},{"pid":"64462640074212f1ef35dfd9c9c300ee3accabb0","tid":1524641,"uid":190406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:50:27.000Z","msg":"開live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93ebe828931307